GET endpoints

GET /books
GET /books/{id}
GET /books/{id}/authors
GET /book/{id}/authors/{id}

Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <token>
Accept: application/json

Status codes
 - 200 OK
 - 400 Bad Request
 - 401 Unauthorized
 - 403 Forbidden
 - 404 Not Found
 - 500 Internal Server Error


 
